longBusinessSummary: CFM Indosuez Wealth Management SA, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the provision of banking and financial solutions to private investors, businesses, institutions, and professionals in Monaco. The company primarily provides wealth management services to help families and entrepreneurs in creating, cultivating, protecting, and passing on wealth. CFM Indosuez Wealth Management SA was founded in 1922 and is headquartered in Monaco. CFM Indosuez Wealth Management SA operates as a subsidiary of CA Indosuez Wealth (Group).
